#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"TH All In One Woo Cart is a perfect choice to display Cart on your website "
"and improve your potential customer’s buying experience. This plugin will "
"add Floating Cart in your website.  Customers can update or remove products "
"from the cart without reloading the cart continuously. It is a fully "
"Responsive, mobile friendly plugin and supports many advanced features."
msgstr ""

